{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/2014/09/11/javascript-workout-at-reasons-to-be-creative-2014/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://blog.aboutme.be"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"8c8a7f77-e2cb-5ded-8478-37ca60623394","excerpt":"After last year’s elevator pitch I was invited back to gave a full talk this year. I wanted to elaborate on javascript and hardware interaction, while linking…","html":"<p>After <a href=\"/2013/09/05/500-people-controlled-my-arduino-at-reasons-to-be-creative-2013/\">last year’s elevator pitch</a> I was invited back to gave a full talk this year. I wanted to elaborate on javascript and hardware interaction, while linking everything to a general theme. I went for “physical workouts”, and built some demos that had to do with that.</p>\n<p>During my talk, I covered different libraries &#x26; hardware platforms:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Bluetooth LE &#x26; <a href=\"https://github.com/noble/noble\">the noble library</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://pulsesensor.com/\">Pulse Sensor</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/sparkdevices/spark-core-wi-fi-for-everything-arduino-compatible\">Spark Core</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://johnny-five.io/\">Johnny-five</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://cylonjs.com/\">Cylon.JS</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://tessel.io/\">Tessel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://docs.spacebrew.cc/\">Spacebrew</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>I wanted to keep things fun and interactive for the audience as well. So I invited people on stage to play heartrate controlled games and dance mat challenges. All built using javascript!</p>\n<p>The people from AnalogFolk captured a nice video of one of the demos:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-resp-iframe-wrapper\" style=\"padding-bottom: 56.25%; position: relative; height: 0; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem\" > <iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/105886639\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen\" allowfullscreen=\"\" style=\" position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; \"></iframe> </div>\n<p>You can <a href=\"https://github.com/wouterverweirder/javascript-workout\">find my presentation and demos on Github</a>. Enjoy!</p>","fields":{"slug":"/2014/09/11/javascript-workout-at-reasons-to-be-creative-2014/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Javascript workout at Reasons to be Creative 2014","date":"09 Sep, 2014","description":false,"tags":["reasons to be creative","arduino","nodejs","javascript"],"cover":{"publicURL":"/static/09526d8d1ed1ef34bfd0067d8792d643/preview.jpg","childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fullWidth","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/09526d8d1ed1ef34bfd0067d8792d643/3c249/preview.jpg","srcSet":"/static/09526d8d1ed1ef34bfd0067d8792d643/3c249/preview.jpg 690w","sizes":"100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/09526d8d1ed1ef34bfd0067d8792d643/956b7/preview.avif 690w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"100vw"},{"srcSet":"/static/09526d8d1ed1ef34bfd0067d8792d643/37026/preview.webp 690w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"100vw"}]},"width":1,"height":1.3333333333333333}}}}},"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/2022/09/28/upload-avatar-duration-strapi-api-user-registration/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Upload an avatar during strapi api user registration","tags":["nodejs","strapi"],"cover":{"publicURL":"/static/68eb0d8195d2fd6a82464b6e00edf059/preview.jpg","childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fullWidth","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/68eb0d8195d2fd6a82464b6e00edf059/0bc76/preview.jpg","srcSet":"/static/68eb0d8195d2fd6a82464b6e00edf059/b0c6e/preview.jpg 750w,\n/static/68eb0d8195d2fd6a82464b6e00edf059/b3149/preview.jpg 1080w,\n/static/68eb0d8195d2fd6a82464b6e00edf059/c56d6/preview.jpg 1366w,\n/static/68eb0d8195d2fd6a82464b6e00edf059/0bc76/preview.jpg 1380w","sizes":"100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/68eb0d8195d2fd6a824